%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as voice.html<br/>(Browser)
    participant Flask as app.py<br/>(Flask Server)
    participant Trans as transcriber.py
    participant Agent as agent_registry.py
    participant Gen as code_generator.py
    participant Store as conversation_store.py
    participant OR as OpenRouter API
    participant FS as File System<br/>+ Git

    Note over User,FS: Phase 1 — Voice Recording & Transcription

    User->>UI: Hold record button & speak
    UI->>UI: MediaRecorder captures WebM audio
    User->>UI: Release button
    UI->>+Flask: POST /api/transcribe (audio blob)
    Flask->>+Trans: transcribe_bytes(audio_bytes)
    Trans->>Trans: Convert WebM → WAV (pydub)
    Trans->>Trans: Base64 encode WAV
    Trans->>+OR: chat.completions.create<br/>(gemini-2.5-flash + audio)
    OR-->>-Trans: Transcribed text
    Trans-->>-Flask: Plain text transcript
    Flask->>+Agent: select_agent(text)
    Agent->>Agent: Parse keywords (gpt/claude/etc.)
    Agent-->>-Flask: agent_id
    Flask->>+Agent: extract_task(text)
    Agent-->>-Flask: Clean task text
    Flask-->>-UI: {text, agent, task}
    UI->>User: Show transcript in editable preview

    Note over User,FS: Phase 2 — Code Generation

    User->>UI: Edit text (optional) + pick model + Send
    UI->>+Flask: POST /api/generate {task, model?, continue_from?}
    Flask->>+Gen: generate_with_model(task, model) or generate_openai/anthropic(task)
    Gen->>Gen: Build system prompt (setup.sh template)
    Gen->>+OR: chat.completions.create<br/>(selected model + system prompt)
    OR-->>-Gen: LLM response (bash script + folder name)
    Gen->>Gen: _parse_response() — extract script, reasoning
    Gen-->>-Flask: {script, folder_name, reasoning, usage}

    Note over User,FS: Phase 3 — Save, Execute & Version

    Flask->>+Store: save_conversation(script, folder_name, task, agent, ...)
    Store->>FS: mkdir conversation/YYYY-MM-DD_HHmm_name/
    Store->>FS: Write setup.sh
    Store->>FS: Execute bash setup.sh (60s timeout)
    FS-->>Store: Generated project files
    Store->>FS: Write metadata.json
    Store->>FS: git add -A && git commit
    Store-->>-Flask: {path, folder, files, script_output, script_success}

    Flask-->>-UI: Full JSON response
    UI->>User: Render files, diffs, output, reasoning

    Note over User,FS: Phase 4 — History & Continuation (optional)

    User->>UI: Browse history / Click "Continue"
    UI->>+Flask: GET /api/history
    Flask-->>-UI: List of all conversations
    UI->>+Flask: GET /api/conversation/:folder
    Flask->>+Store: get_conversation(folder)
    Store->>FS: Read files + git log + git diff
    Store-->>-Flask: Full conversation data
    Flask-->>-UI: {metadata, files, git_log, git_diff}
